  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The breakfast buffet here has a huge amount of choice with fresh fruit, <span>pancakes, jams, bread, cakes and biscuits, salami produced on the family farm or delicious cheeses, omelettes and eggs. </span>Everything is home made. Breakfast is served from 7.30am - 11.30am, so you can have a nice long lie in if you want. </p>
<p>There's a <span>corner dedicated to people with dietary requirements, intolerance's and celiac disease, with gluten free products, vegan, dairy free and vegetarian options. Please let us know of any dietary requirements at the time of booking.  </span></p>
<p>The hotel offer flexible <span>à la carte </span><span>dining from 12.30pm - 10.30pm (pay in hotel). Most of the products used in the tasty dishes are locally sourced. The meats come from their butchery and some products straight from their farm. There's loads of tasty options on the menu. </span><span>Early meals for children are available on request. </span></p>
<p>If you fancy dining out some evenings, the staff will be very happy to make recommendations, from pizzerias to typical Aosta Valley restaurants. There's lots to choose from in Champoluc. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
